name: The Abandoned Oma Opa House Lasem
description:
@PopItself / ig: @heritagepop / twitter: @PopItSelf collaboration with @boiboisiboi / twitter : @soemantrigelar

 50% of sales for #KyleMinuk via #LasemHeritageFoundation ( #KyleMinuk has lived in this house since 1977 as helper and housekeeper)

At first it was a video documentation of an old house ( Oma Opa House) in Lasem, Central Java which is approximately 200 years old in a mixed Chinese, Javanese and European architectural style and once appeared on Instagram @heritagepop with a massive attack's black milk as backsound - for the promotion of #DiscoverLasemPop and is now a work of nft art  collaboration

This nft can be used for entrance tickets to Oma Opa House Lasem 

This is part of the Heritage Preservation Movement in Lasem
